div.div:
This risque romantic comedy story centers on Eita, an introvert mecha otaku high schooler who has a crush on the school's most popular girl Makina. When Eita finds Makina at her doorstep, he is flustered, and even more so when Makina reveals her secret: that she is a "sexaroid" robot designed for pleasure, and she is asking Eita to conduct some repairs on her discreetly. While Makina immediately tries to make a move on Eita physically, Eita struggles to contain himself, while also hiding her secret.
(Source: Anime News Network, edited)
Sousou no Frieren: ●● no Mahou Part 2

A new batch of the ●● no Mahou shorts released monthly in the lead up to the TV anime's second season, starting with #12. The MUZIK TIGER franchise centers on Toffee, a tiger that lives in the forest with other animal friends. (Source: Anime News Network)
Secret Mission: Sennyuu Sousakan wa Zettai ni Makenai!

Riko Ikazuchi is an undercover agent who keeps her true identity hidden while infiltrating different crime scenes. She is posing as a newlywed with her junior colleague Noma in an apartment where a criminal organization is based. (Source: Coolmic) Note: Episode 1 received an advanced distribution on AnimeFesta on September 8th, 2023. The start date reflects the start of the regular series broadcasting.
